Name: Suki's Spooky Romance
About the game: Suki the cat needs help to become a full fledged catgirl again. Three other catgirls need help finding their lost master. Jacob needs help finding the love he never knew he wanted. One adventure through a haunted mansion full of dimensional doors should fix it all! This is a classic style RPG with an amusing story, hand drawn enemies, and a catchy musical score. You'll guide a team of four catgirls through a haunted mansion. Lead them into strange, unknown dimensions to battle ghosts and monsters for...parts. Rescue the great master of magic, and Suki will be a catgirl forever. Poor Jacob won't know what hit him.
